<div class="relative min-h-screen bg-gray-900 py-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/volta.jpeg?height=800&width=1200"
        alt=""
        class="h-full w-full object-cover opacity-20"
      />
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Contactanos</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-6 text-gray-300">
          We use an agile approach to test assumptions and connect with the needs of your audience early and often.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="mt-12 rounded-lg bg-white p-8 shadow-xl">
        <form class="space-y-6">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div>
              <label for="firstName" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Nombre</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                name="firstName"
                id="firstName"
                placeholder="Bonnie"
                required
                class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary sm:text-sm"
              />
            </div>
  
            <div>
              <label for="lastName" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Apellido</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                name="lastName"
                id="lastName"
                placeholder="Green"
                required
                class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary sm:text-sm"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
  
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div>
              <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Email</label>
              <input
                type="email"
                name="email"
                id="email"
                required
                placeholder="ejemplo@gmail.com"
                class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary sm:text-sm"
              />
            </div>
  
            <div>
              <label for="phone" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Telefono</label>
              <input
                type="tel"
                name="phone"
                id="phone"
                required
                placeholder="0984802345"
                class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary sm:text-sm"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
  
          <div>
            <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Tu mensaje</label>
            <textarea
              id="message"
              name="message"
              rows="4"
              required
              placeholder="Deja un comentario..."
              class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary sm:text-sm"
            ></textarea>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
            Al enviar este formulario usted acepta nuestro <a href="#" class="text-blue-500 underline"> términos y condiciones</a> y nuestra <a href="#" class="text-blue-500 underline">politica de privacidad</a>.
        </p> 
  
        <button
        type="submit"
        class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
      >
        Enviar
      </button>
        </form>
      </div>
  
      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium text-white">Correo Electrónico:</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-300">Email us for general queries, <br> including marketing and partnership opportunities.</p>
          <a href="mailto:hello@flowbite.com" class="mt-4 block text-white hover:underline">Alessandrovolta@gmail.com</a>
        </div>
  
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium text-white">Llamenos:</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-300">Call us to speak to a member of our team. <br> We are always happy to help.</p>
          <a href="tel:+1(646)786-5060" class="mt-4 block text-white hover:underline">+593 968392559</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br>
  
